title: 033 - The Winchester Boat Club
description: On today's show, the guys discuss what they did over the weekend with the beautiful weather in Indianapolis which included the boys from The Pub finally all moved into their new house and some issues that came up trying to mount a TV, creating a gang (SHAHK GANG) on Grand Theft Auto 5 and trying to recruit as many new members as possible. The guys also each chat about some of the new things they watched this weekend, and unearth a revelation about Connor's life back home that will shatter what how they view him. Keep sending questions to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram to help get us keep getting through the quarantine. Stay safe out there and enjoy.
